{"tid":1551073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係加拿大撚，琴晚感謝咁多位巴絲，今日WINNIPEG手足又做到野。","createTime":"2019-09-07T22:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T23:40:12.000Z","uid":23480,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"13532104abaa59828827aadd6775f5e8797dc4a8","tid":1551073,"uid":23480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T22:41:37.000Z","msg":"winnipeg係加拿大中部一個細城市，人口得70萬，大概就係一個沙田咁多人，出名凍，係好撚凍，冬天可以凍成六個月。<br />\n<br />\n但係咁惡劣嘅生存環境之下，一樣有一班香港人，不畏強權，不畏小粉紅，企出黎，做加拿大撚榜樣，擺支旗出黎，同鬼佬做文宣，要俾鬼佬知道香港，要俾鬼佬知chinaiz，要係加拿大搞大佢，對抗共產黨。<br />\n<br />\n今日係正個home game球賽開波前，企正係個主要出入路口，同33500個睇波既鬼佬，講解香港既情況同吸引下鬼佬眼球。<br />\n<br />\n班兄弟一路擺一路嗌，一路收到好多鬼佬響咹支持，仲有鬼佬一齊嗌口號，每個兄弟都感動到流哂眼淚！再一次證明，抗爭路上香港人唔係孤單一個，最起碼係winnipeg唔係！係加拿大唔係！<br />\n<br />\n你問我地有無見到小粉紅？緊係有，我地有收到三隻來自中國的中指同紅媒既招呼。你地俾中指，我地緊係嗌free hong kong free china<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，我地從不孤單！<br />\n時代革命，光復香港！<br />\n我地香港人，海外本地，一齊撐落去！<br />\n我地要打贏共產黨！<br />\n要對住佢地往死裏打！<br />\n香港人，加油！<br />\n加港同行，光復香港。<br />\n一陣908，踩上領事館！<br />\n我要香港民主及人權法！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVNWhhC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVNWhhC.png&h=616de950&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6k8ivCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6k8ivCD.jpg&h=67b3306a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhSje4j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhSje4j.jpg&h=bf2e786f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOUEZwd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOUEZwd.png&h=65485cde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtoN8pz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtoN8pz.jpg&h=35fc06dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qhpd3XV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqhpd3XV.jpg&h=6b6eab82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywdRQCX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywdRQCX.jpg&h=ea8c8b54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34e7b14e9a11a966cfa52992a99c170e94b98394","tid":1551073,"uid":254843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T22:43:52.000Z","msg":"多謝加拿大手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c521007a3f221b30f7050265279644f610ffb91","tid":1551073,"uid":272028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:09:29.000Z","msg":"in Winnipeg we trust"},{"pid":"4701f4850a0111d22605f4ddc87050779aa41a84","tid":1551073,"uid":232456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d413528256dc752e816c89c48389c64fe678cc2","tid":1551073,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:35:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"018471682366446dc87f54831926475f4a35a509","tid":1551073,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:37:44.000Z","msg":"用電話影電話<br />\n<br />\nGenius<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea0b3b2cea9bd3e74d9ad03cb3181ef95c0e751","tid":1551073,"uid":295673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:39:50.000Z","msg":"多謝手足，好感動！！"},{"pid":"ebbd9b67ef605deee3f49a87b5e838c73ecb1c4f","tid":1551073,"uid":46457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:40:51.000Z","msg":"多謝巴絲們咁落力！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: